name: @nkmr-jp/api-to-go
author: nkmr-jp <nkmr.git@gmail.com>

scripts.sync-version: npm version from-git --no-git-tag-version && git add package.json && git commit -m ":bookmark: [skip ci] v$(cat package.json | jq -r .version)"
scripts.setup: yarn install && yarn fetch && npm -f link && exec $SHELL -l

description: Convert REST API's JSON payload to Golang struct.
